cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with object recognition in videos using deep neural networks. 
2. cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper mentions the application of the proposed approach for robotic perception. 
3. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is another possible category as the paper uses Long Short-Term Memory (LSTM) deep networks for learning motion dependencies. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as the paper deals with the application of deep neural networks for object recognition. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is another possible category as the paper deals with recognition of objects in short videos.
